{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Quickstart","title":"Quickstart","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/GettingStarted"]},{"anchor":"How-to-Guides","title":"How-to Guides","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToAddAPermanentLicense","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToPresentTheUI","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToPreviewAndTest"]},{"anchor":"Reference","title":"Reference","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/ServiceReference","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/MockServiceReference","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/UIComponentsReference"]},{"anchor":"Explanation","title":"Explanation","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/PlatformBehavior","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/EntitlementMapping"]},{"anchor":"Service-Layer","title":"Service Layer","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/RevenueCatPaywallService"]},{"anchor":"Testing","title":"Testing","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/MockRevenueCatPaywallService"]},{"anchor":"Enumerations","generated":true,"title":"Enumerations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/RevenueCatPaywall"]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"RevenueCat adapter for Swidux’s ","type":"text"},{"code":"PaywallPlugin","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". Implements ","type":"text"},{"code":"PaywallService","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" against ","type":"text"},{"code":"Purchases.shared","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ships a controllable mock for previews and tests, and pairs with ","type":"text"},{"code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" for drop-in ","type":"text"},{"code":"PaywallView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"CustomerCenterView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" presentation.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"}],"role":"collection","roleHeading":"Framework","title":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","externalID":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","symbolKind":"module"},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"anchor":"Overview","level":2,"text":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"},{"text":" is the adapter between RevenueCat’s SDK and Swidux’s purchase-agnostic paywall plugin. The plugin owns paywall state (presentation flags, current entitlement, async progress); this package translates RevenueCat’s ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomerInfo"},{"text":" into the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"EntitlementSnapshot"},{"text":" the plugin expects, and surfaces the live ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"customerInfoStream"},{"type":"text","text":" so entitlement changes propagate without polling."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Two products ship together:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"RevenueCatPaywallService"},{"type":"text","text":" (the live "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallService"},{"type":"text","text":" conformer) and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MockRevenueCatPaywallService"},{"type":"text","text":" (a controllable preview \/ test conformer)."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"revenueCatPaywall(isPresented:)"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"revenueCatCustomerCenter(isPresented:)"},{"type":"text","text":", drop-in SwiftUI view modifiers that wrap RevenueCatUI with platform-aware presentation, plus a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"revenueCatPaywall(state:send:)"},{"type":"text","text":" convenience that composes both."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The flow:"}]},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":["View → store.send(.paywall(.request(reason:)))","  → PaywallPlugin sets isPresented = true","  → revenueCatPaywall observes the change, presents RevenueCatUI.PaywallView","  → user purchases → Purchases.shared.customerInfoStream yields a new CustomerInfo","  → RevenueCatPaywallService maps it to EntitlementSnapshot","  → PaywallPlugin reduces .customerInfoUpdated, sets isPro = true","  → store.paywall.isGateSatisfied flips, gated UI unlocks"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The plugin and the adapter stay decoupled: the plugin doesn’t know about RevenueCat, and the adapter doesn’t know about your action tree."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[[]]},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/MockServiceReference":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/MockServiceReference","abstract":[{"text":"API reference for ","type":"text"},{"code":"MockRevenueCatPaywallService","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" — a controllable ","type":"text"},{"cod